{"tid":524325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（月經）血液存量降至警戒水平 紅十字會緊急呼籲各界捐血","createTime":"2018-01-09T12:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T18:18:08.000Z","uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1d12e2105bb0843ada9b68dee0d68ebf7f4645","tid":524325,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"香港紅十字會輸血服務中心今日表示，因全港醫院血液使用量一直高企，<span style=\"color: red;\">（因為廢老太多？）</span>目前中心各類血型血液存量已下降至警戒水平，緊急呼籲市民捐血。<br />\n<br />\n中心指，捐血人數已有相當長時間未能達到每日1,100人的目標，<span style=\"color: red;\">（要返工，不了）</span>加上剛過去的聖誕新年長假期令捐血人士前來捐血意欲減低，另由於全港醫院的內科病床使用率上升，<span style=\"color: red;\">（長假期梗係多支那人落黎香港免費醫病啦！）</span>血液需求現時處於極高水平，血液供應現正面對巨大壓力<span style=\"color: red;\">，（叫班唔使做一落黎就咬綜援既新移民捐lor笨七）</span>中心呼籲社會各界齊心立即以行動回應，支持捐血。"},{"pid":"24141f753e911bd275ac8d47e233f70c37e217e9","tid":524325,"uid":150098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"叫啲公墓員每日捐返包先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6445f7086c316f470f7f9407c0c7bed08a9c0f","tid":524325,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6bcaba7998c982497b1561705cbe63daed5c96","tid":524325,"uid":1221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"返工都已經賣緊血仲叫我損？不了。"},{"pid":"71f46fb4a0ca3a880d3ff564eb82f01833bf825e","tid":524325,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"28c2ddf76799f98245f5e4f92674ccd7cf889ff9","tid":524325,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"個個月都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc87127451b5dd2ccec50740efefca3e1cb18442","tid":524325,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T06:01:25.000Z